# My Properties вЂ” Owner/Agent Listing Feature

## Overview

Add a **"My Properties"** tab to the Customer Dashboard visible only to `owner` and `agent` roles. This tab lets them:
- **List** their submitted properties (Pending / Active / Expired)
- **Create** a new property listing (submitted for admin approval)
- **View Detail** of any property (status, rejection reason, etc.)
- **Update Status** (hide/unhide, mark as rented/sold/occupied)
- **Delete** a property

The flow matches the backend docs exactly:  
`Owner/Agent submits в†’ status: pending в†’ Admin approves/rejects в†’ status: active/rejected`

