## Proposed Changes

### 1. RTK Query API Slice (NEW)

#### [NEW] `src/REDUX_FEATURES/REDUX_SLICES/customerPropertyApi/customerPropertyApi.js`

Covers all 6 property CRUD endpoints + 4 media/document endpoints:

| Hook | Method | Endpoint |
|---|---|---|
| `useCreatePropertyMutation` | POST | `/customer/properties` |
| `useGetMyPropertiesQuery` | GET | `/customer/properties?page&limit&status` |
| `useGetPropertyByIdQuery` | GET | `/customer/properties/:id` |
| `useUpdatePropertyMutation` | PUT | `/customer/properties/:id` |
| `useUpdatePropertyStatusMutation` | PATCH | `/customer/properties/:id/status` |
| `useDeletePropertyMutation` | DELETE | `/customer/properties/:id` |
| `useUploadPropertyMediaMutation` | POST | `/customer/properties/:id/media` |
| `useDeletePropertyMediaMutation` | DELETE | `/customer/properties/:id/media/:mediaId` |
| `useUploadPropertyDocumentMutation` | POST | `/customer/properties/:id/documents` |
| `useDeletePropertyDocumentMutation` | DELETE | `/customer/properties/:id/documents/:documentId` |

Uses the **same `axiosBaseQuery` pattern** as `customerAuthApi` вЂ” no new axios instance needed.

