### 6. Create Property Modal (Multi-step Form)

#### [NEW] `src/Components/Customer_Segment/Tabs/Properties/CreatePropertyModal.jsx`

**Step flow (4 steps):**

| Step | Fields |
|---|---|
| 1. Basic Info | listingType, propertyType, title, description, condition, constructionStatus, furnishing, facing, flooringType, ownershipType |
| 2. Size & Specs | area (value + unit), price, maintenance, bedrooms, bathrooms, floorNo, totalFloors, waterSupply, powerBackup, parkingType |
| 3. Features | securityFeatures (checkboxes), amenities (checkboxes), connectivity (checkboxes), nearbyFacilities (checkboxes) |
| 4. Location + Listing Specifics | location fields (fullAddress, city, state, pincode, lat, lng) + conditional: `rentalDetails` (if "For Rent") OR `saleDetails` (if "For Sell") |

**Design:** Dark-themed modal with step progress bar, matching admin segment visual language.  
Submit в†’ calls `useCreatePropertyMutation` в†’ toast success в†’ close modal в†’ refetch list.

